<section id="slide-2">
<h2 id="2"><a id="org32695cc"></a><span class="section-number-2">2</span> Reveal.js plugins</h2>
<ul>
<li>Reveal.js has lots of plugins</li>
<li>Some can be installed and activated with oer-reveal
<ul>
<li>Notice non-defaults here:
<ul>
<li>TOC progress plugin <b>missing</b></li>
<li>Only jump plugin present
<ul>
<li>Press slide number, then enter to jump</li>

</ul></li>
<li>Audio autoplay set to <code>true</code>
<ul>
<li>No audio file embedded; inspect HTML code to see this</li>

</ul></li>

</ul></li>

</ul></li>

</ul>
